                type="document" xml:id="d20">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In telegram 896, March 16, from Seoul, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_BEO1"
                        >Ellis O. Briggs</persName> transmitted the text of a letter, dated March
                    11, from President <persName corresp="#p_RS1">Rhee</persName> to President
                        <persName corresp="#p_EDD1">Eisenhower</persName>. The text of the letter
                    was excluded from this publication at the request of the Republic of Korea
                    Government. For the full text of President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName>’s reply to <persName corresp="#p_RS1"
                    >Rhee</persName>’s letter, see telegram 748, March 20, to Seoul, <ref
                        target="#pg_44">page 44</ref>. Regarding Ambassador <persName
                        corresp="#p_BEO1">Briggs</persName>’ <pb facs="0062" n="36" xml:id="pg_36"/>
                    delivery of the President’s reply to <persName corresp="#p_RS1">Rhee</persName>
                    on March 22, see telegram 926, March 22, from Seoul, <ref target="#pg_48">page
                        48</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
